    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced pepper</strong> and<strong> sliced onion</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until everything is beginning to soften</p><p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse your <strong>red kidney beans</strong>, then boil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/984.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/984.-step-2-x400.jpg",
