            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add your <strong>ground cumin</strong> and <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can’t handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [100ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>drained red kidney beans</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until a thick sauce remains – this is your<strong> enchilada filling</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/984.-step-3-x200.jpg",
