            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Place the <strong>enchiladas</strong> in an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, with the seam face down</p><p>Top with the <strong>remaining enchilada filling</strong> and the <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven and cook for 10-12 min or until the cheese is golden and melted</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
