            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the enchiladas are in the oven, trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Combine the<strong> ground smoked paprika </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>mayo</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and mix to combine – this is your<strong> smoky mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
